{"tid":1873113,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「武肺」2人未尋回警將發通緝令「2月10日」","createTime":"2020-02-10T12:41:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-10T12:55:31.000Z","uid":143865,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1d672eadaa3bfbd242104eb528876248d5d1e4a2","tid":1873113,"uid":143865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T12:41:43.000Z","msg":"一張相都冇公佈比大眾點相<br />\n啲無膽狗會唔會去搵都成問題<br />\n香港人自求多福<br />\n<br />\n內文：<br />\n<br />\n食物及衛生局長陳肇始今日（10日）在記者會表示，強制檢疫令實施至今，有2人因未有按照命令留在指定居所，警方將發出通緝令。<br />\n<br />\n【17:53】食物及衛生局副秘書長（食物）鄭鍾偉表示，未能聯絡的人當中，部分是正在睡覺，但稍後已成功聯絡，另有一至兩名稱外出購買食物及必需品，他們已被警告在強制檢疫期間不應離開住所。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200210/s00001/1581324536797/【武漢肺炎】9人違強制檢疫令外出-2人未尋回警將發通緝令\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200210%2Fs00001%2F1581324536797%2F%E3%80%90%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%919%E4%BA%BA%E9%81%95%E5%BC%B7%E5%88%B6%E6%AA%A2%E7%96%AB%E4%BB%A4%E5%A4%96%E5%87%BA-2%E4%BA%BA%E6%9C%AA%E5%B0%8B%E5%9B%9E%E8%AD%A6%E5%B0%87%E7%99%BC%E9%80%9A%E7%B7%9D%E4%BB%A4&d=u5wkwi0qRaq%2FdbVqa5yG4ZwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=eaad7501\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200210%2Fs00001%2F1581324536797%2F%E3%80%90%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%919%E4%BA%BA%E9%81%95%E5%BC%B7%E5%88%B6%E6%AA%A2%E7%96%AB%E4%BB%A4%E5%A4%96%E5%87%BA-2%E4%BA%BA%E6%9C%AA%E5%B0%8B%E5%9B%9E%E8%AD%A6%E5%B0%87%E7%99%BC%E9%80%9A%E7%B7%9D%E4%BB%A4&h=5e8996ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200210/s00001/1581324536797/【武漢肺炎】9人違強制檢疫令外出-2人未尋回警將發通緝令</a>"},{"pid":"589f56b05b8a8bc90e8fb6bd37b9f1c8ab04b8be","tid":1873113,"uid":143865,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T12:54:25.000Z","msg":"大家仲傻下傻下咁 隨時你身邊有社區炸彈呀"},{"pid":"2deaf022d904d7f4529c3be8d76be8900c5f9c8a","tid":1873113,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedB